.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.scored.co/post/Z8cJk4cqlWi9.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/POzDW4oA3QTNRog4.png", "width": 768, "content-type": "png", "height": 273}], "blurhash": "U55X[c%jo*tB.Ax{tUtB9GtAx_f.D*t8tSRo", "full_resolution": [311, 874]}, "title": "\ud83c\udfc5 \ud835\udc16\ud835\udc08\ud835\udc0d\ud835\udc0d\ud835\udc08\ud835\udc0d\ud835\udc06: The Supreme Court has just ALLOWED Alabama Republicans to \ud835\ude40\ud835\ude47\ud835\ude44\ud835\ude48\ud835\ude44\ud835\ude49\ud835\ude3c\ud835\ude4f\ud835\ude40 a majority-Black congressional district ahead of the midterms...", "last_comment_created": 1780457765296, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 1, "score_up": 69, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASsia2tD2", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 30, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8656374, "raw_content": "There's literally no excuse for not checking the person who is pale, altered and weak and says \"I've been stabbed\" for injuries.\n\nThe police pathologist claims there's no way he could have survived. That's bullshit. He was 3 miles from a trauma center. If he were a cop, the police would have scooped him up and blasted to the ER in under 5 minutes. They would have done CPR the whole way.\n\nIn my ER, he'd have gotten the full monty. Anyone 'dead' for less than 10 minutes from penetrating trauma gets everything, especially if you're young.\n\nHe'd be stripped, flipped and have two large bore IVs and decompressive needles in his chest in under 3 minutes. In the next three minutes he'd have been Intubated and be halfway through 2U of O negative blood. Within 10 minutes of him hitting the door, I'd have his chest open, his pericardium open and I'd be massaging his heart, maybe twisting off his injured lung. We'd be on our way to the operating room.\n\nHe might still die, but he'd have a decent chance at making it.", "author": "SuperDuperBasedMD", "created": 1780468638188, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Hunter_loves_2_feet", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Henry Nowak didn't have to die", "last_comment_created": 1780475272768, "content": "<p>There's literally no excuse for not checking the person who is pale, altered and weak and says &quot;I've been stabbed&quot; for injuries.</p>\n<p>The police pathologist claims there's no way he could have survived. That's bullshit. He was 3 miles from a trauma center. If he were a cop, the police would have scooped him up and blasted to the ER in under 5 minutes. They would have done CPR the whole way.</p>\n<p>In my ER, he'd have gotten the full monty. Anyone 'dead' for less than 10 minutes from penetrating trauma gets everything, especially if you're young.</p>\n<p>He'd be stripped, flipped and have two large bore IVs and decompressive needles in his chest in under 3 minutes. In the next three minutes he'd have been Intubated and be halfway through 2U of O negative blood. Within 10 minutes of him hitting the door, I'd have his chest open, his pericardium open and I'd be massaging his heart, maybe twisting off his injured lung. We'd be on our way to the operating room.</p>\n<p>He might still die, but he'd have a decent chance at making it.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 10, "score_up": 30, "is_edited": true, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2061994765768356183", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsia2t4m", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 35, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8656354, "raw_content": "", "author": "mohel", "created": 1780466127948, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsia2t4m.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/slocumfortexas/status/2061994765768356183", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Tonight at the \u201cRally Against Rednecks\u201d in North Texas, there were plenty of real \u201cRednecks\u201d there to confront those who had planned this idiotic rally, and almost no willing protesters there to actually do the rallying for the \u201cRally Against Rednecks\u201d.", "last_comment_created": 1780466127948, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 0, "score_up": 35, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": false, "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 9, "created": 1780452836000, "id": "2061994765768356183", "video": {"preview": "https://pbs.twimg.com/amplify_video_thumb/2061994665599983616/img/XRXeNbcJddkUfUsu.jpg", "mpeg": "https://video.twimg.com/amplify_video/2061994665599983616/pl/V8wNyHMWZ8XbKRdX.m3u8?v=cfc", "aspectRatio": [16, 9], "heightRatio": 56, "type": "video/mp4", "url": "https://video.twimg.com/amplify_video/2061994665599983616/vid/avc1/480x270/R2UBwZgaiIUF3m2M.mp4"}, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1635085729050001411/DDlpgYke_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Tom Slocum for Texas \ud83c\uddfa\ud83c\uddf8", "username": "slocumfortexas"}, "content": "Tonight at the \u201cRally Against Rednecks\u201d in North Texas, there were plenty of real \u201cRednecks\u201d there to confront those who had planned this idiotic rally, and almost no willing protesters there to actually do the rallying for the \u201cRally Against Rednecks\u201d. \n\nGo figure \ud83d\ude02", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 359}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsia2t8q", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 33, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8656360, "raw_content": "", "author": "Stormeyworld13", "created": 1780466683503, "profile_picture": "m8BKqYZhtAQn", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Metal4Freedom", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.scored.co", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsia2t8q.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.scored.co/post/RU1Wnzc69h5k.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/GajsQ0BzSmfunQQA.png", "width": 420, "content-type": "png", "height": 768}], "blurhash": "ULRo]V9buOtkR5IBNdgN?]nMMJX9X-x]VYH?", "full_resolution": [1974, 1080]}, "title": "Does this look like a blue state? ", "last_comment_created": 1780472080641, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 17, "score_u